{"tid":2291172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"年初元朗西鐵站連儂牆混戰　警追查近10個月拉3男","createTime":"2020-11-18T14:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T14:29:44.000Z","uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9878a18779d17c3c248aa674b6259c4ac4d4de09","tid":2291172,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"今年1月30日晚上近11時，元朗西鐵站連儂牆發生大混戰，約10名大漢追打在場貼文宣市民，據網上拍得短片，多名男女被打至瞓地，地上遺下血漬，場面混亂，其中一名姓朱(30歲)女子更遭人搶去一部約值1萬元手機；警方亦於晚上11時左右接報，指有人在上址打架。經調查後，共4男2女(16至42歲)受傷，當中年紀最輕的為16歲男童，案件列傷人及搶劫，案件由新界北總區反三合會行動組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n人員經深入調查後，今日(18日)上午在元朗、大埔及上水拘捕3名本地男子(22至44歲)，涉嫌傷人。3名被捕男子現正被扣留調查。"},{"pid":"a9a1dfe942910dbf02058a5613d405da20810c1e","tid":2291172,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stAzDDu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstAzDDu.png&h=83b4a787&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e96db617785a8cee54b2edca2ad8e42c9c434764","tid":2291172,"uid":108016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"藍屍打人叫混戰<br />\n<a href=\"http://On.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOn.cc&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5oZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=4ebd1926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">On.cc</a> 真係on9"},{"pid":"1cd1ef4466609c70d5a3849d286f62c0b0f815df","tid":2291172,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"小心原告變被告"}]}